      "content": "that makes sense. can u get a bit more specific with the grooming part though? like for hair and stuff. i have some clients who might struggle with traditional 'neatness' if they have different textures or styles. what should i tell them to avoid if they want to ensure they don't seem too casual or unprofessional to the execs?",
